structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
PUBLIC WORKS IN CITIES OTHER THAN THE FIRST CLASS

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 233, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1980. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3562a-1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Dedication of public ways -- Plats or maps filed only when accepted and recorded -- Cities of fourth class are repealed.
